[external][hsushulong][hsushulong@gmail.com]
[external][mlgmxyysd][mlgmxyysd@meowcat.org]## Install
[external][mlgmxyysd][mlgmxyysd@meowcat.org]
[internal][howard20181][40033067+Howard20181@users.noreply.github.com]1. Install Magisk v24+
[external][howardwu20][HowardWu20@outlook.com]2. (For Riru flavor) Install [Riru](https://github.com/RikkaApps/Riru/releases/latest) v26.1.7+
[internal][vvb2060][vvb2060@gmail.com]3. [Download](#download) and install LSPosed in Magisk app
[internal][vvb2060][vvb2060@gmail.com]4. Reboot
[internal][vvb2060][vvb2060@gmail.com]5. Open LSPosed manager from notification
[internal][vvb2060][vvb2060@gmail.com]6. Have fun :)
[external][mlgmxyysd][mlgmxyysd@meowcat.org]
