[external][mlgmxyysd][mlgmxyysd@meowcat.org]## For Developers
[external][hsushulong][hsushulong@gmail.com]
[external][kidonng][44045911+kidonng@users.noreply.github.com]Developers are welcome to write Xposed modules with hooks based on LSPosed Framework. A module based on LSPosed framework is fully compatible with the original Xposed Framework, and vice versa, a Xposed Framework-based module will work well with LSPosed framework too.
[external][hsushulong][hsushulong@gmail.com]
[external][mlgmxyysd][mlgmxyysd@meowcat.org]- [Xposed Framework API](https://api.xposed.info/)
[external][mlgmxyysd][mlgmxyysd@meowcat.org]
[external][wanghan1995315][wanghan1995315@gmail.com]We use our own module repository. We welcome developers to submit modules to our repository, and then modules can be downloaded in LSPosed.
[external][mlgmxyysd][mlgmxyysd@meowcat.org]
[external][wanghan1995315][wanghan1995315@gmail.com]- [LSPosed Module Repository](https://github.com/Xposed-Modules-Repo)
